
 This patch fixes a text sizing problem in the tray-monitor.
 It fixes bug #1219.

 Apply it to version 2.4.4 with:

 cd <bacula-source>
 patch -p0 <2.4.4-tray-sizing.patch
 ./configure <your options>
 make
 ...
 make install


